cc4a7dde9dc71fb34fdec2269d06f","tid":488373,"uid":15572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實男仔話放低，係咪真心？有個男追緊我，但之前佢鍾意咗個女仔好耐，表白兩次都失敗。佢話而家已經無感覺，但唔知點解硬係有條刺喺心裏面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真心都唔出奇，以我自己為例，試過晒都真係唔得，就會完完全全放低，唔會再返轉頭。"},{"pid":"dee7ae89051a00220a9b324788c0c7a4a5c4b6fc","tid":488373,"uid":144468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮嘜撚野情聖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n俾我呻吟下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d2bb05e35845bda047a8a75a8a45bbf1d38e1e","tid":488373,"uid":111811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T09:02:39.000Z","msg":"明知冇結果 都放棄唔到<br />\n可能時辰未到"},{"pid":"06f8252fb93d425424269e5cdf82c88751adab38","tid":488373,"uid":129506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:22:13.000Z","msg":"如果比耐性就追到，咁個個都追到啦<br />\n<br />\n我又比耐性係咪我都有份"}]}